data.value: How to add new image or animation images to visual js project : Manual copy folder with new images files to folder res/ After copying click Builds resources button. Access image or images of animation (PNG sequence) like this : example : we added folder crazyFrog intro res/ RESOURCE.

data.name: label15.Text
data.value: Every object created in editor mode will be placed in starter/visual.js ( first startVisual editor after job in web page editor click GENERATE visual-js ) . Copy code from starter/visual.js and put in SOME_NAME.js and load in run.js

data.value:
goto https://nodejs.org and install in classic windows style system NEXT ... FINISH And you will get node in your console .
Create two new folders and click CREATE APPLICATION button Select one folder for server ( out of www ) and secund folder for client part ( in www )
1) Install next modules :
In node.js command prompt enter next lines ( - g global )
npm install mysql npm install delivery npm install express npm install mkdirp npm install socket.io npm install nodemailer@0.7.0
Looking good , now you have no need for other languages . Make JS code for any solution.
